    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LIGMANAUTS!!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ballsy take on the &quot;Play with your Friends&quot; genre. Ligmanauts  has you rolling around and grabbing your friends by the fistful in co-op platforming mayhem for up to 8-players.      </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore Dense Worlds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scour the Ligma-verse for Rocket Juice and fuel-up your Rocket to blast off into new densely packed worlds. Overcome challenges designed to test your crew’s coopitism:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steer something that does not need eight people to steer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack on top of friends until someone slowly leans the wrong way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a leap of faith trusting a player who shouldn’t be trusted.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116440/extras/3cb45efeb4ec56f8863df6f8e4e25933.poster.avif?t=1772082647\" width=596 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116440/extras/3cb45efeb4ec56f8863df6f8e4e25933.webm?t=1772082647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116440/extras/3cb45efeb4ec56f8863df6f8e4e25933.mp4?t=1772082647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classic Platforming Action</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement is fast, tactile, and playful. Roll, bounce, grab, swing, jump, and boost through physics-driven challenges that reward creativity and momentum over strict perfection.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playground Hub</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between challenges, vibemax in a shared hub – a persistent playground where you unlock toys, microgames, and cosmetics. Mess around together, rizz up with your new toys and prep for the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116440/extras/d77b4e468368ea7918ddeb386b9cc16a.poster.avif?t=1772082647\" width=596 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116440/extras/d77b4e468368ea7918ddeb386b9cc16a.webm?t=1772082647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116440/extras/d77b4e468368ea7918ddeb386b9cc16a.mp4?t=1772082647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer for up to 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local co-op split screen for up to 4 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple themed worlds with replayable scenarios</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-driven movement built for expressive, cooperative play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shared progression and a persistent Playground Hub</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmetic unlocks and emotes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original Liquid DnB soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfectly baked Balsagna</p></li></ul>",
